author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Highwoods Prices $350 Mln Of 4.125 Pct Notes Due 2028
text:
Feb 22 (Reuters) - Highwoods Properties Inc:
* HIGHWOODS PRICES $350 MILLION OF 4.125% NOTES DUE 2028 * HIGHWOODS PROPERTIES - OPERATING PARTNERSHIP, PRICED A $350 MILLION OFFERING OF 4.125% UNSECURED NOTES​
* HIGHWOODS PROPERTIES INC - NOTES ARE DUE MARCH 15, 2028 AND WERE PRICED TO YIELD 4.271%​
* HIGHWOODS PROPERTIES INC - ‍NET PROCEEDS FROM SALE OF NOTES WILL BE USED TO REPAY OR REPURCHASE OUTSTANDING DEBT​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
